                                <h2>Gas By Gas</h2>
                                <p>A key player in Sri Lanka’s energy market, Gas By Gas is the largest importer and distributor of LPG in the country, holding the majority market share of domestic, industrial and commercial LPG markets in Sri Lanka. As a State Owned Enterprise, the primary objective of the Company is to facilitate access to affordable and clean energy.</p>
                                <p>Gas By Gas fulfils this national obligation by importing LPG from international suppliers and distributing it island wide, through a network of dealers and distributors, to ensure easy access to LPG, for all socio-economic categories. Through this process Gas By Gas supports millions of households by providing an affordable, clean energy source for cooking.</p>
                                <p>Thousands of small businesses with LPG for a range of business applications from food production to manufacturing, and larger industries for industrial applications. By establishing a network of dealers, distributors,  the Company has also created a new form of self-employment for thousands of people across the country.</p>
                                <h2>Domestic LP Gas</h2>
                                <p>The Domestic Sector is the largest market segment of the company, which is focused on Sri Lankan households. 80% of the total L.P. gas sales of The Company arise from this segment.</p>
                                <p>The wide usage of our product stems from the ability to use it safely, conveniently and economically.</p>
                                <p>The Domestic Sector provides several categories of cylinders, which vary on the weight of L.P. gas. The cylinder sizes offered by Gas by Gas include 12.5 kg, 5kg and 2.3 kg. Most of the cylinders are used in the households for domestic cooking purposes.</p>
                                <p>Gas by Gas has always been driven by a passion for service excellence that is reflected in every aspect of our product offering. Our ability to understand and respond to changing customer needs while offering them a tangible economic benefit is a critical factor that defines our mode of operations.</p>
                                <p>For the convenience of customers, Gas by Gas has introduced a four-digit number 1311 and enable customers to order their LPG requirements in a timely and swift manner.</p>
